headlines.description: George Kiernan scored 17 points and Shawn Anderson scored 13 and Navy rallied at the end and beat Loyola (Md.) 62-56 on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Navy's late 15-2 run carries it past Loyola (MD) 62-56

headlines.description: Khalil Small scored 26 points with 10 rebounds, four assists and three steals, Sandy Cohen added 31 points and Green Bay raced out of the regular season with a 107-97 defeat of Detroit Mercy on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Small, Cohen help Green Bay defeat Detroit 107-97

headlines.description: Ike Smith scored 25 points with five 3-pointers, Tookie Brown scored all of his 16 points in the second half, and third-place Georgia Southern beat Texas State 81-77 on Saturday to split the season series.
headlines.shortLinkText: Smith scores 25, Georgia Southern beats Texas State 81-77

headlines.description: Otis Livingston II had seven of his 22 points in overtime and assisted on Ian Boyd's game winning basket to help George Mason beat Massachusetts 78-76 on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Boyd's buzzer-beating layup lifts Mason over UMass in OT

headlines.description: Malique Trent-Street scored 16 points on 6-for-9 shooting to lead Hampton to a 57-38 win over Morgan State on Saturday.
Trae Bell-Haynes had 19 points, including six in the final four minutes, and six assists and Payton Henson added 17 points and nine rebounds to help Vermont beat Stony Brook 69-60 on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Bell-Haynes, Vermont use late run to beat Stony Brook 69-60

headlines.description: Hassan Hussein made a layup late in the game to give Florida International the lead for good in a 67-64 win over Rice on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Hussein puts Florida International over Rice 67-64

headlines.description: Jalen Johnson sank four 3-pointers and finished with 20 points to lead Saint Louis past George Washington for a 62-53 win Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Saint Louis holds off George Washington 62-53

headlines.description: Tyrell Gumbs-Frater drilled six from beyond the arc to total 24 points and lead Coastal Carolina to an 88-81 win over Arkansas State in Sun Belt Conference action on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Coastal Carolina hangs out to beat Arkansas State 88-81

headlines.description: Jemerrio Jones had 15 points, a career-high 23 rebounds and seven assists and New Mexico State never trailed in its 82-58 win over Missouri-Kansas City on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jones has 15 points, 23 rebounds; New Mexico St. beats UMKC

headlines.description: Oscar Frayer and Alessandro Lever had 16 points apiece as Grand Canyon managed to survive a late push by Utah Valley 60-59 on Saturday night to give coach Dan Majerle his 100th victory in five years at Grand Canyon.
headlines.shortLinkText: Grand Canyon survives late push to beat Utah Valley 60-59

headlines.description: Bogdan Bliznyuk drilled a late 3-pointer to put Eastern Washington in front for good, sending the Eagles to a 74-69 Big Sky Conference victory over Idaho State Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Bliznyuk, Eastern Washington hold off Idaho State, 74-69

headlines.description: Juwan Gray had 18 points on Saturday night and scored the go-ahead points on a 3-point play with 13 seconds left to help San Diego beat San Francisco 64-61 in the conference season finale for both teams.
headlines.shortLinkText: San Diego steals 1 away from San Francisco 64-61

headlines.description: Justin James scored 26 points and Wyoming snapped Fresno State's five-game win streak with a 78-68 victory on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: James scores 26 points, leads Wyoming past Fresno St. 78-68

nowFeed.headline:
I followed Grayson Allen closely since his high school days. A fierce  competitor who gave it his all. He never had one issue on or off the court. I called Duke's game last year when Grayson Allen had his tripping incident. Tonight on senior night in a win over North Carolina I loved listening to Maria Taylor's post-game interview with Allen. 
What does Duke mean to you? 
" It means everything to me, it's my love and my passion. " Allen said. 
I call that growing up.
